---
alwaysApply: true
---

The Maximo version selected by the user must be loaded from `knowledge/versions/`
at pipeline runtime (via `VERSION_MAP`) and injected into the analyzer and
generator system prompts dynamically.

Never hardcode Maximo version facts in Python or agent prompt templates.
Version-specific behaviour lives in knowledge files, not in code.

MAS 8.x (`mas-8`) is disabled in MVP — show "Coming soon"; do not enable until Milestone 5.

Requirement traceability is document-level: `source_ref` must be the source filename only.
